{
  "stem": "3475.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somebody told us that he was in a group of people that they circled around, you know, and shoved him into a-- I think it was a streetcar or something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took him away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, he wouldn't be away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was the first thing that I lost-- was my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about 17 at that time, so-- that time about 17.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a tragedy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- and then they started to tighten the ghetto more and more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was still sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at one time, we even went out of the ghetto to work for Polish farmers-- at the beginning of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm going back now a little bit, when they first closed the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You could still get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we went out to work for Polish farmers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I worked for a few months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then we saw that there was a war coming out between Germany and Russia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As I was standing-- the, the place that I was working was the Polish Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was-- you could see the German Army massing and coming into Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we thought we'd better come and go back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- like I say, in those days, we didn't know that it's going to be so terrible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and then we-- I had-- I had-- we had relatives that we stayed with.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they owned, like, a wood-- a small-sized wood mill where they made wood molding and boards.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
